        public TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX()
        Create an object that holds a null TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX.
        The call isNull() on the object created will returns true.
          TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX obj = new TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX();
  (obj == null) <=> false
  obj.isNull() <=> true
        To creates a new TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX, use the static "constructor" : 
          TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX obj = TAG_FLAC_CUE_TRACK_INDEX.allocate();
        See Also:
        allocate()
